<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
No spoilers here, please. <p>
NO SPOILERS HERE! 
</p>
<p>
A Paladin is a warrior-priest at the service of <a class="nonexistent" href="./Tulkas">Tulkas</a>. As such, his duty is to ever be vigilant against the forces of evil and even seek and destroy those monsters which are evil to the core, especially the foulest spawns of hell. Luckily, his quest is eased by the blessing bestowed by Tulkas himself. 
</p>
<p>
Starting stat modifiers, starting Skills, innate abilities and starting equipment: Please see the in-game help. 
</p>
